    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204620/extras/a1b4c645c94f97bc6054dff26126174f.poster.avif?t=1755239149\" width=600 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204620/extras/a1b4c645c94f97bc6054dff26126174f.webm?t=1755239149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入 King's Blade 的黑暗英雄奇幻世界——一款受《野蛮人柯南》宇宙及《战斧》《怒之铁拳》等传奇街机游戏启发的经典清版动作游戏！掌控 皇家之刃 的精英战士，在 巴加尼亚帝国 的大军中杀出血路！在史诗战斗中粉碎敌人，探索致命之地，直捣敌军首都核心。支持最多4名玩家的本地合作模式，或添加AI战士加入你的队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204620/extras/5159439c4c13e8894ac97fb5632a1c40.poster.avif?t=1755239149\" width=600 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204620/extras/5159439c4c13e8894ac97fb5632a1c40.webm?t=1755239149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6位独特英雄。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12个多样化关卡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含连招、场景武器、法术和特殊攻击的深度战斗系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多4名玩家的本地合作模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与AI合作模式。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204620/extras/597b6f2d676fe94be563869fc97feb2f.poster.avif?t=1755239149\" width=600 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204620/extras/597b6f2d676fe94be563869fc97feb2f.webm?t=1755239149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
